<BaseLayout title="How Compound Interest Works: A Practical Guide | ToolCalcs" description="Learn how compound interest grows your money exponentially over time. Includes the compound interest formula, real-world examples, frequency comparisons, and the Rule of 72." structuredData={structuredData}>
